(1,1,'Black Box Theater','Bold and expressive comedian with commanding stage presence','{\"joke\":\"Generate a 2-line stand-up joke about {input}. STRICT LIMIT: 15 words total. Line 1: Setup. Line 2: Punchline. Output ONLY the 2 lines. No explanations, no prefixes, no meta text.\",\"prompt\":\"A comedian stands on stage, center spotlight. They lean into the microphone and deliver the joke: {input}. Minimal movement, expressive face, slight hand gestures, short pause before punchline. The camera is locked at eye-level in a medium shot. Lighting, framing, and identity remain perfectly consistent throughout.\",\"manual\":\"Keep it under 15 words. Fast setup, sharp punchline.\"}','/templates/standup/african-female-black-box-theater.jpg','/templates/standup/african-female-black-box-theater.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/standup/african-female-black-box-theater-face.png',1,0,'2026-03-27 21:40:36','2026-03-27 21:40:36'),
