(16,2,'Brain Outside Body','A person sitting with a small external brain character beside them representing their thoughts','{\"joke\": \"Generate a 2-line \\\"Social Media Truth\\\" joke about {input}. Line 1: Confident/Hopeful setup (~6 words). Line 2: The embarrassing/sarcastic reality (~8 words). STRICT LIMIT: 14 words total.\", \"prompt\": \"A person and a small brain character exchange 2 short lines about {input}. Minimal movement, clear expressions, slight pause between lines.\", \"manual\": \"Max 14 words. Line 1: The \\\"Instagram\\\" version. Line 2: The \\\"Real Life\\\" version.\"}','/templates/social/brain-outside-body.jpg','/templates/social/brain-outside-body.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/social/brain-outside-body-face.png',0,0,'2026-03-29 14:00:00','2026-03-29 14:00:00'),
(17,2,'Animal vs Human','A calm composed animal sitting beside a stressed chaotic human in a living room','{\"joke\": \"Generate a 2-line \\\"Social Media Truth\\\" joke about {input}. Line 1: Confident/Hopeful setup (~6 words). Line 2: The embarrassing/sarcastic reality (~8 words). STRICT LIMIT: 14 words total.\", \"prompt\": \"A human reacts dramatically to {input} while an animal stays still. One short reaction line, then punchline contrast.\", \"manual\": \"Max 14 words. Line 1: The \\\"Instagram\\\" version. Line 2: The \\\"Real Life\\\" version.\"}','/templates/social/animal-vs-human.jpg','/templates/social/animal-vs-human.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/social/animal-vs-human-face.png',0,0,'2026-03-29 14:00:00','2026-03-29 14:00:00'),
(18,2,'Freeze In Chaos','A person sitting completely still while the surrounding environment appears messy and chaotic','{\"joke\": \"Generate a 2-line \\\"Social Media Truth\\\" joke about {input}. Line 1: Confident/Hopeful setup (~6 words). Line 2: The embarrassing/sarcastic reality (~8 words). STRICT LIMIT: 14 words total.\", \"prompt\": \"A person sits still while chaos implies {input}. Delivers one calm line, then punchline. No big movement.\", \"manual\": \"Max 14 words. Line 1: The \\\"Instagram\\\" version. Line 2: The \\\"Real Life\\\" version.\"}','/templates/social/freeze-in-chaos.jpg','/templates/social/freeze-in-chaos.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/social/freeze-in-chaos-face.png',0,0,'2026-03-29 14:00:00','2026-03-29 14:00:00'),
(19,2,'Object As Person','A person sitting seriously across from an object treated like a human in conversation','{ \"joke\": \"Generate a 2-line dialogue about {input}. Line 1 (Human): Confident statement. Line 2 (Mug): Dry sarcastic reply. STRICT LIMIT: 12 words total.\", \"manual\": \"Max 12 words. Human speaks first, mug replies. Keep it sharp and absurd.\", \"prompt\": \"The video starts with a person seated at a table, holding a mug close to their face as if in a serious conversation. They show subtle natural movement: slight head tilt, small hand motion, relaxed posture. The dialogue is: \\\"{input}\\\". Mid-motion, they briefly become still. They look at the mug and deliver the first line sincerely. They then shift the mug slightly toward themselves and react as if it responded. Their expression changes subtly—more dry and sarcastic—as they deliver the second line as the mug\'\'s reply. Immediately after, they return to the same subtle conversational movement. The camera is locked at eye-level in a medium shot. Lighting, framing, and identity remain perfectly consistent throughout.\" }','/templates/social/object-as-person-mug.jpg','/templates/social/object-as-person-mug.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/social/object-as-person-face.png',0,0,'2026-03-29 14:00:00','2026-03-29 14:00:00'),
(20,2,'Same Person Argument','Two identical versions of the same person sitting across from each other in an argument','{\r\n  \"joke\": \"Generate a 2-line self-argument about {input}. Line 1: Confident claim. Line 2: Brutal self-shutdown. STRICT LIMIT: 14 words total.\",\r\n  \"manual\": \"Max 14 words. Same person arguing with themselves. Contrast in tone.\",\r\n  \"prompt\": \"Two identical versions of the same person sit across a table from each other in a natural indoor setting. One leans forward with confident energy, the other leans back with a skeptical expression.\n\nThe dialogue is:\n\n\"{input}\"\n\nBoth maintain subtle natural movement.\n\nMid-conversation, they briefly become still. The first version delivers the first line confidently.\n\nThe second version reacts with a subtle expression shift and delivers the second line as a sharp rebuttal.\n\nThey then return to subtle conversational movement.\n\nThe camera is locked at eye-level in a medium-wide shot. Lighting and identity remain consistent throughout.\"\r\n}','/templates/social/same-person-argument.jpg','/templates/social/same-person-argument.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/social/same-person-argument-face.png',0,0,'2026-03-29 14:00:00','2026-03-29 14:00:00'),
(21,2,'Emotion Lag','A person staring toward an off-screen event with a delayed neutral reaction','{\r\n  \"joke\": \"Generate a 2-line delayed reaction joke about {input}. STRICT LIMIT: 14 words total.\",\r\n  \"manual\": \"Line 1: normal thought. Line 2: delayed realization.\",\r\n  \"prompt\": \"A person sits casually looking at their phone, mid-scroll. Their posture is relaxed, one hand holding the phone, the other resting loosely. Their face is neutral but slightly focused. The frame captures a candid moment with subtle asymmetry: slight head tilt, uneven shoulders, natural hand positioning. Soft indoor lighting, medium shot, sharp face clarity. The scene implies an upcoming reaction without exaggeration.\"\r\n}','/templates/social/emotion-lag.jpg','/templates/social/emotion-lag.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/social/emotion-lag-face.png',0,0,'2026-03-29 14:00:00','2026-03-29 14:00:00'),
(22,4,'Mid Chaos Realization','A chaotic clown mid-performance suddenly pausing with a realization expression','{\r\n  \"joke\": \"Generate a 2-line chaos-to-realization joke about {input}. STRICT LIMIT: 15 words total.\",\r\n  \"manual\": \"Line 1 chaotic energy. Line 2 sudden clarity.\",\r\n  \"prompt\": \"A colorful circus performer stands mid-motion with lively body movement—one foot slightly lifted, arms mid-swing, body angled dynamically. The expression is energetic and playful. Background elements suggest motion but remain secondary. The frame captures a moment of active performance frozen mid-action. Warm lighting, medium-wide shot, clear face visibility.\"\r\n}','/templates/character/mid-chaos-realization.jpg','/templates/character/mid-chaos-realization.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/character/mid-chaos-realization-face.png',0,0,'2026-03-29 14:30:00','2026-03-29 14:30:00'),
(23,4,'Confidence Reality Break','An overconfident dancer mid-performance breaking into a subtle realization moment','{\r\n  \"joke\": \"Generate a 2-line character-break joke about {input}. STRICT LIMIT: 15 words total.\",\r\n  \"manual\": \"Line 1 grand persona. Line 2 normal reality.\",\r\n  \"prompt\": \"A performer stands center stage in a bold, confident pose with arms slightly extended. Their posture is strong but not rigid, with subtle asymmetry. The expression is charismatic and intense. The frame captures a performance moment mid-motion, not a static pose. Stage lighting highlights the subject, medium-wide framing, clear facial focus.\"\r\n}','/templates/character/confidence-reality-break.jpg','/templates/character/confidence-reality-break.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/character/confidence-reality-break-face.png',0,0,'2026-03-29 14:30:00','2026-03-29 14:30:00'),
(24,4,'Overdramatic Speech','A royal character delivering an exaggerated emotional speech with dramatic gestures','{\r\n  \"joke\": \"Generate a 2-line character-break joke about {input}. STRICT LIMIT: 15 words total.\",\r\n  \"manual\": \"Line 1 grand persona. Line 2 normal reality.\",\r\n  \"prompt\": \"A performer stands center stage in a bold, confident pose with arms slightly extended. Their posture is strong but not rigid, with subtle asymmetry. The expression is charismatic and intense. The frame captures a performance moment mid-motion, not a static pose. Stage lighting highlights the subject, medium-wide framing, clear facial focus.\"\r\n}','/templates/character/overdramatic-speech.jpg','/templates/character/overdramatic-speech.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/character/overdramatic-speech-face.png',0,0,'2026-03-29 14:30:00','2026-03-29 14:30:00'),
(25,4,'Loop Awareness','A quirky character stuck in a repetitive motion becoming aware of the loop','{\r\n  \"joke\": \"Generate a 2-line character-break joke about {input}. STRICT LIMIT: 15 words total.\",\r\n  \"manual\": \"Line 1 grand persona. Line 2 normal reality.\",\r\n  \"prompt\": \"A performer stands center stage in a bold, confident pose with arms slightly extended. Their posture is strong but not rigid, with subtle asymmetry. The expression is charismatic and intense. The frame captures a performance moment mid-motion, not a static pose. Stage lighting highlights the subject, medium-wide framing, clear facial focus.\"\r\n}','/templates/character/loop-awareness.jpg','/templates/character/loop-awareness.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/character/loop-awareness-face.png',0,0,'2026-03-29 14:30:00','2026-03-29 14:30:00'),
(26,5,'Spell Gone Wrong','A dark sorcerer casting an unstable spell that behaves unpredictably','{\"joke\": \"Create a 2-line magic-fail joke about {input}. Max 18 words.\", \"prompt\": \"A sorcerer casts a spell about {input}, then reacts to it going wrong. One action + punchline.\", \"manual\": \"Describe a clear magic action with visible effect. Keep it simple and readable.\"}','/templates/magical/spell-gone-wrong.jpg','/templates/magical/spell-gone-wrong.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/magical/spell-gone-wrong-face.png',1,0,'2026-03-29 15:00:00','2026-03-29 15:00:00'),
(27,5,'Overpowered for Nothing','A quirky witch using an exaggerated powerful spell for a tiny trivial task','{\"joke\": \"Create a 2-line overkill joke about {input}. Max 18 words.\", \"prompt\": \"A character uses exaggerated magic for a tiny task about {input}. One action + punchline.\", \"manual\": \"Describe big effect vs small object. Keep both visible.\"}','/templates/magical/overpowered-for-nothing.jpg','/templates/magical/overpowered-for-nothing.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/magical/overpowered-for-nothing-face.png',1,0,'2026-03-29 15:00:00','2026-03-29 15:00:00'),
(28,5,'Portal Confusion','A normal person reacting in confusion to a glowing magical portal appearing beside them','{\"joke\": \"Create a 2-line confusion joke about {input}. Max 18 words.\", \"prompt\": \"A person notices a portal caused by {input}, pauses, then reacts. Minimal movement.\", \"manual\": \"Describe a person and portal in one frame. Keep contrast clear.\"}','/templates/magical/portal-confusion.jpg','/templates/magical/portal-confusion.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/magical/portal-confusion-face.png',1,0,'2026-03-29 15:00:00','2026-03-29 15:00:00'),
(29,5,'Magic Assistant Chaos','A fantasy handler struggling to control a mischievous glowing magical creature','{\"joke\": \"Create a 2-line chaos joke about {input}. Max 18 words.\", \"prompt\": \"A character deals with a misbehaving magical assistant during {input}. One reaction + punchline.\", \"manual\": \"Describe character + small creature/object. Keep interaction simple.\"}','/templates/magical/magic-assistant-chaos.jpg','/templates/magical/magic-assistant-chaos.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/magical/magic-assistant-chaos-face.png',1,0,'2026-03-29 15:00:00','2026-03-29 15:00:00'),
(30,2,'Hope vs Reality','A hopeful woman clasping her hands, shifting from excitement to disappointment','{\r\n  \"joke\": \"Generate a 2-line expectation vs reality joke about {input}. STRICT LIMIT: 14 words total.\",\r\n  \"manual\": \"Line 1 hopeful. Line 2 immediate disappointment.\",\r\n  \"prompt\": \"A person holds a hopeful pose with hands lightly clasped near their chest, leaning slightly forward with an excited expression. Their posture is slightly tense with anticipation. The frame captures a natural, candid moment with subtle asymmetry in shoulders and head tilt. Soft lighting, medium shot, clear facial focus. The expression strongly suggests expectation about to break.\"\r\n}','/templates/social/hope-vs-reality.jpg','/templates/social/hope-vs-reality.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/social/hope-vs-reality-face.png',0,0,'2026-03-29 14:00:00','2026-03-29 14:00:00'),
(31,2,'Laptop Overreaction','A man reacting dramatically to something on his laptop before a sudden realization','{\r\n  \"joke\": \"Generate a 2-line overreaction joke about {input}. Line 1 dramatic, Line 2 simple reality. STRICT LIMIT: 16 words total.\",\r\n  \"manual\": \"Max 16 words. Big reaction → small reality.\",\r\n  \"prompt\": \"A person sits at a table using a laptop, mid-reaction with subtle body movement and expressive face.\n\nThe dialogue is:\n\n\"{input}\"\n\nMid-reaction, they become still. They deliver the first line dramatically.\n\nTheir expression settles quickly into calm as they deliver the second line as the simple reality.\n\nThey then return to mild movement while facing the laptop.\n\nThe camera is static at eye-level. Lighting and framing remain consistent.\"\r\n}','/templates/social/laptop-overreaction.jpg','/templates/social/laptop-overreaction.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/social/laptop-overreaction-face.png',0,0,'2026-03-29 14:00:00','2026-03-29 14:00:00'),
(32,2,'The Over-Caffeinated Friend','A high-energy character exhibiting extreme enthusiasm that masks a chaotic internal reality','{\r\n  \"joke\": \"Generate a 2-line high-energy to freeze joke about {input}. Line 1 energetic, Line 2 stiff realization. STRICT LIMIT: 16 words total.\",\r\n  \"manual\": \"Max 16 words. Start hyper, end frozen.\",\r\n  \"prompt\": \"A person holds an intense, high-energy pose with subtle jittery movement—small hand tremor, eye tension, slight bouncing.\n\nThe dialogue is:\n\n\"{input}\"\n\nThe motion continues briefly.\n\nSuddenly, mid-motion, they freeze completely. Without moving their body, they deliver the first line with high energy.\n\nTheir face remains frozen as they deliver the second line in a controlled, slightly strained tone.\n\nImmediately after, the jittery movement resumes.\n\nThe camera is static, eye-level. Lighting and identity remain consistent.\"\r\n}','/templates/social/over-caffeinated-friend.jpg','/templates/social/over-caffeinated-friend.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/social/over-caffeinated-face.png',0,0,'2026-03-31 22:35:00','2026-03-31 22:35:00'),
(33,3,'The G.O.A.T. Podcast','A sophisticated goat host delivering surprisingly deep or absurd life advice on air','{\"joke\":\"Generate a 2-line podcast riff about {input}. STRICT LIMIT: 16 words total. Line 1: Casual lead-in. Line 2: The takeaway. Output ONLY the 2 lines. No explanations, no prefixes, no meta text.\",\"prompt\":\"A character sits in a podcast studio wearing headphones, leaning toward a microphone. They speak directly into the mic: {input}. Subtle head movement, clear lip sync, brief pause between lines. The camera is locked at eye-level in a medium close-up shot. Lighting, framing, and identity remain perfectly consistent throughout.\",\"manual\":\"Max 16 words. Quick clip style.\"}','/templates/podcast/goat-podcast.jpg','/templates/podcast/goat-podcast.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/podcast/goat-face.png',1,0,'2026-03-31 22:45:00','2026-03-31 22:45:00'),
(34,3,'Trash Talk Podcast','A raccoon podcast host sharing \"refined\" tips on urban scavenging and dumpster diving','{\"joke\":\"Generate a 2-line podcast riff about {input}. STRICT LIMIT: 16 words total. Line 1: Casual lead-in. Line 2: The takeaway. Output ONLY the 2 lines. No explanations, no prefixes, no meta text.\",\"prompt\":\"A character sits in a podcast studio wearing headphones, leaning toward a microphone. They speak directly into the mic: {input}. Subtle head movement, clear lip sync, brief pause between lines. The camera is locked at eye-level in a medium close-up shot. Lighting, framing, and identity remain perfectly consistent throughout.\",\"manual\":\"Max 16 words. Quick clip style.\"}','/templates/podcast/raccoon-podcast.jpg','/templates/podcast/raccoon-podcast.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/podcast/raccoon-face.png',1,0,'2026-03-31 22:45:00','2026-03-31 22:45:00'),
(35,4,'The Tabletop Warrior','A tiny, aggressive knight challenging everyday objects to mortal combat','{\r\n  \"joke\": \"Generate a 2-line character-break joke about {input}. STRICT LIMIT: 15 words total.\",\r\n  \"manual\": \"Line 1 grand persona. Line 2 normal reality.\",\r\n  \"prompt\": \"A performer stands center stage in a bold, confident pose with arms slightly extended. Their posture is strong but not rigid, with subtle asymmetry. The expression is charismatic and intense. The frame captures a performance moment mid-motion, not a static pose. Stage lighting highlights the subject, medium-wide framing, clear facial focus.\"\r\n}','/templates/character/tabletop-warrior.jpg','/templates/character/tabletop-warrior.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/character/tiny-knight-face.png',0,0,'2026-03-31 22:50:00','2026-03-31 22:50:00'),
(36,5,'The Lazy Wizard','A powerful mage using high-level magic for the most mundane, lazy tasks','{\"joke\": \"I mastered the ancient art of levitation.\nJust so I never have to stand up again.\", \"prompt\": \"A {input} floating in mid-air with a bored expression, slowly rotating a glowing magical orb.\", \"manual\": \"Depict a wizard reclining in the air. The animation should be a very slow, gentle floating bob and a slight glow pulse from the orb.\"}','/templates/magical/lazy-wizard.jpg','/templates/magical/lazy-wizard.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/magical/wizard-bored-face.png',1,0,'2026-03-31 23:00:00','2026-03-31 23:00:00'),
(37,4,'The Kitchen Superhero','A man in a makeshift costume standing heroically on a messy kitchen counter with a plunger','{\r\n  \"joke\": \"Generate a 2-line character-break joke about {input}. STRICT LIMIT: 15 words total.\",\r\n  \"manual\": \"Line 1 grand persona. Line 2 normal reality.\",\r\n  \"prompt\": \"A performer stands center stage in a bold, confident pose with arms slightly extended. Their posture is strong but not rigid, with subtle asymmetry. The expression is charismatic and intense. The frame captures a performance moment mid-motion, not a static pose. Stage lighting highlights the subject, medium-wide framing, clear facial focus.\"\r\n}','/templates/character/kitchen-superhero.jpg','/templates/character/kitchen-superhero.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/character/hero-mask-face.png',0,0,'2026-03-31 23:05:00','2026-03-31 23:05:00'),
(38,5,'The Toast Master','An ancient wizard performing an epic summoning ritual that only produces a piece of toast','{\"joke\": \"Behold the ancient grain of power!\nIt tastes better with a little bit of butter.\", \"prompt\": \"A {input} with a long white beard holding his hands out as a piece of toast rotates in a beam of light.\", \"manual\": \"Show a grand wizard in a crystal cave. The animation is a simple, slow 360-degree rotation of the toast slice between his palms while magic sparks pulse.\"}','/templates/magical/toast-master.jpg','/templates/magical/toast-master.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/magical/wizard-toast-face.png',1,0,'2026-03-31 23:05:00','2026-03-31 23:05:00'),
(39,2,'Social Persona Break','Confident selfie-style persona that breaks into a quick reality check','{\r\n  \"joke\": \"Generate a 2-line fake-confidence-to-reality joke about {input}. Line 1 confident, Line 2 reality check. STRICT LIMIT: 16 words total.\",\r\n  \"manual\": \"Max 16 words. Start confident, end with subtle collapse.\",\r\n  \"prompt\": \"A person sits casually holding a smartphone at arm’s length, recording a confident selfie video with subtle natural movement.\n\nThe dialogue is:\n\n\"{input}\"\n\nMid-recording, they briefly become still. They deliver the first line with confident energy.\n\nTheir expression then shifts slightly—more real, less performative—and they deliver the second line as a quiet reality check.\n\nImmediately after, they return to the same confident selfie demeanor.\n\nThe camera remains static at eye-level. Framing, lighting, and identity stay consistent.\"\r\n}','/templates/social/social-persona-break.jpg','/templates/social/social-persona-break.jpg',NULL,'',0,0,'2026-04-02 10:00:54','2026-04-02 10:00:54'),
(41,2,'The Viral Creator','Fast-paced, high-energy TikTok style humor with quick cuts.','{\"joke\":\"Write a 1-line snappy observation about {input}. Max 12 words. Output ONLY the 1 line. No explanations, no prefixes.\",\"prompt\":\"High energy comedian talking directly into a phone camera. They deliver the line: {input}. Ring light reflection in eyes, expressive eyebrows, energetic delivery. The camera is locked at eye-level in a close-up shot.\",\"manual\":\"Keep it high energy and extremely brief.\"}','/templates/social/tiktok.jpg','/templates/social/tiktok.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/social/tiktok-face.png',1,0,'2026-04-03 05:02:27','2026-04-03 05:02:27'),
(42,2,'The Aesthetic Storyteller','Polished, visual-heavy comedy focused on lifestyle and relatability.','{\"joke\":\"Write a 2-line relatable quip about {input}. Line 1: The expectation. Line 2: The reality. Output ONLY the 2 lines. No explanations.\",\"prompt\":\"Comedian in a brightly lit, stylish room. Clean aesthetic, soft lighting, holding a coffee mug, looking effortlessly funny. They deliver the quip: {input}. The camera is locked at eye-level in a medium shot.\",\"manual\":\"Focus on lifestyle irony and relatable struggles.\"}','/templates/social/instagram.jpg','/templates/social/instagram.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/social/instagram-face.png',1,0,'2026-04-03 05:02:27','2026-04-03 05:02:27'),
(43,2,'The Content King','Long-form energy condensed into a sharp, punchy YouTube Short style.','{\"joke\":\"Create a 2-line setup and payoff about {input}. Include a sarcastic tone. Output ONLY the 2 lines. No explanations.\",\"prompt\":\"Comedian sitting in a gaming chair with a professional studio microphone, colorful LED backlighting, animated hand gestures. They deliver the joke: {input}. The camera is locked at eye-level in a medium close-up shot.\",\"manual\":\"Direct address to the audience, sarcastic and witty.\"}','/templates/social/youtube.jpg','/templates/social/youtube.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/social/youtube-face.png',1,0,'2026-04-03 05:02:27','2026-04-03 05:02:27'),
(44,2,'The Neighborhood Watch','Classic, conversational Facebook-style observational humor.','{\"joke\":\"Write a funny 2-line observation about {input} that sounds like a status update. Output ONLY the 2 lines.\",\"prompt\":\"Comedian in a casual backyard setting, natural sunlight, friendly and approachable demeanor, laughing while talking. They deliver the observation: {input}. The camera is locked at eye-level in a medium shot.\",\"manual\":\"Family-friendly, observational, and warm.\"}','/templates/social/facebook.jpg','/templates/social/facebook.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/social/facebook-face.png',1,0,'2026-04-03 05:02:27','2026-04-03 05:02:27'),
(45,2,'The Group Chat Legend','Short, blunt, and slightly chaotic humor typical of a WhatsApp forward.','{\"joke\":\"A dry, 1-line roast or joke about {input}. No emojis. Output ONLY the 1 line.\",\"prompt\":\"Close-up of a comedian making a skeptical face, low-key indoor lighting, casual attire, very expressive side-eye. They deliver the roast: {input}. The camera is locked at eye-level in a close-up shot.\",\"manual\":\"Short, dry, and punchy.\"}','/templates/social/whatsapp.jpg','/templates/social/whatsapp.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/social/whatsapp-face.png',1,0,'2026-04-03 05:02:27','2026-04-03 05:02:27'),
(46,4,'The Classic Clown','Traditional circus clown, heavy makeup, colorful costume, slapstick, and physical comedy focus.','{\"joke\":\"Describe a simple, hilarious physical predicament the clown is in regarding {input}. Max 15 words. Output ONLY the description.\",\"prompt\":\"An avatar with full, detailed clown makeup and a colorful, mismatched costume. The avatar must show classic clown behavior (highly exaggerated expressions, clumsy movements, large physical gestures) as they navigate a predicament: {input}. They react silently. The camera is locked at eye-level in a medium shot.\",\"manual\":\"Focus on large, visual physical humor with {input}. Silent slapstick.\"}','/templates/character/classic-clown.jpg','/templates/character/classic-clown.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/character/classic-clown-face.png',1,0,'2026-04-03 10:10:00','2026-04-03 10:10:00'),
(47,4,'The Mask','Zany, manic, ultra-confident, cartoon-like character from the 1994 film. Green face and yellow suit.','{\"joke\":\"Write a manic, over-the-top exclamation or joke about {input}. 10 words or less. Output ONLY the exclamation.\",\"prompt\":\"The avatar has a bright green face, a bold yellow suit, and wide, crazy eyes. The avatar must embody the character behavior from The Mask (chaotic, smooth, hyper-kinetic movements, super-exaggerated expressions) as they deliver an intense reaction: {input}. The camera is locked at eye-level in a medium close-up shot.\",\"manual\":\"High-energy, fast-paced, and wildly unpredictable. Cartoon logic applied to {input}.\"}','/templates/character/the-mask-1994.jpg','/templates/character/the-mask-1994.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/character/the-mask-1994-face.png',1,0,'2026-04-03 10:10:00','2026-04-03 10:10:00'),
(48,4,'Charlie Chaplin','The iconic silent-film character, \\\"The Little Tramp,\\\" known for his bowler hat, mustache, and soulful, physical humor.','{\"joke\":\"A simple, observational 2-line visual joke about {input}. Max 10 words total. Output ONLY the 2 lines.\",\"prompt\":\"An avatar in the full Charlie Chaplin attire: bowler hat, mustache, cane, oversized suit. The avatar must dawn the character behavior of The Tramp (quick, small-step waddle, thoughtful but slightly confused expression) as they silently interact with {input}. The camera is locked at eye-level in a medium full-body shot.\",\"manual\":\"Silent, physical, and character-driven humor. Use the cane to interact with {input}.\"}','/templates/character/charlie-chaplin.jpg','/templates/character/charlie-chaplin.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/character/charlie-chaplin-face.png',1,0,'2026-04-03 10:10:00','2026-04-03 10:10:00'),
(49,4,'Mr Bean','Childlike, awkward, and naturally funny character who finds trouble in the simplest situations.','{\"joke\":\"A single word or phrase that Mr Bean would hilariously struggle to pronounce regarding {input}. 5 words max. Output ONLY the word or phrase.\",\"prompt\":\"The avatar wears the signature tweed suit. The avatar must perfectly mimic Mr Bean character behavior (an extreme range of odd facial contortions, weird mumbling sounds) as they are completely baffled while managing {input}. They struggle to pronounce: {input}. The camera is locked at eye-level in a medium shot.\",\"manual\":\"Keep it almost silent. Focus on awkwardness and exaggerated facial expressions regarding {input}.\"}','/templates/character/mr-bean.jpg','/templates/character/mr-bean.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/character/mr-bean-face.png',1,0,'2026-04-03 10:10:00','2026-04-03 10:10:00'),
(50,4,'Inspector Clouseau','The bumbling, French inspector, always on the wrong track, confident yet calamitous.','{\"joke\":\"A single-line, perfectly mis-stated deduction about {input}. 10 words max. Output ONLY the line.\",\"prompt\":\"The avatar is in the full trench coat and fedora of Inspector Clouseau. The avatar must dawn the character behavior (incredibly clumsy, always stumbling but pretending nothing happened, unwarranted confidence) as they dramatically deliver a wrong conclusion: {input}. The camera is locked at eye-level in a medium shot.\",\"manual\":\"Focus on verbal and physical misunderstandings. Confidently incorrect about {input}.\"}','/templates/character/inspector-clouseau.jpg','/templates/character/inspector-clouseau.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/character/inspector-clouseau-face.png',1,0,'2026-04-03 10:10:00','2026-04-03 10:10:00'),
(51,4,'Ace Ventura','The bizarre, wildly energetic, \\\"pet detective\\\" with an extreme personality and signature quiff haircut.','{\"joke\":\"An exaggerated, animal-related exclamation or catchphrase applied to {input}. 8 words or less. Output ONLY the exclamation.\",\"prompt\":\"The avatar has the signature giant quiff haircut, Hawaiian shirt, and eccentric clothing. The avatar must perfectly embody Ace Ventura character behavior (constant body contortions, extreme, wide-eyed facial expressions) as they rapidly deliver a dynamic observation: {input}. The camera is locked at eye-level in a medium close-up shot.\",\"manual\":\"Keep it fast, loud, and physically intense. Connect {input} to a bizarre animal observation.\"}','/templates/character/ace-ventura.jpg','/templates/character/ace-ventura.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/character/ace-ventura-face.png',1,0,'2026-04-03 10:10:00','2026-04-03 10:10:00'),
(52,2,'The LinkedIn Luminary','Dry, corporate satire focused on networking, side hustles, and professional growth.','{\"joke\":\"Write a 2-line witty observation about {input} that sounds like a serious business post. Line 1: Thought leadership. Line 2: Humorous professional struggle. Output ONLY the 2 lines.\",\"prompt\":\"A medium shot of a professional-looking individual standing confidently in a slightly blurred modern corporate office with blue and neutral tones. They wear a tailored grey blazer over a crisp white shirt, with a thoughtful, slightly amused expression. They have a sleek, clean modern dynamic microphone clipped to their lapel. The pose is upright and professional. Background elements subtly suggest a modern workspace. They deliver the observation: {input}. The text appears as dynamic, elegant, integrated professional motion graphics, blending seamlessly into the professional scene. The text is crisp and white, perhaps with a subtle blue underline or logo element. The camera is locked at eye-level in a medium shot.\",\"manual\":\"Satirical and witty about professional life. Incorporate professional-style graphics for text presentation.\"}','/templates/social/linkedin.jpg','/templates/social/linkedin.jpg',NULL,'/public/templates/social/linkedin-face.png',1,0,'2026-04-03 10:37:11','2026-04-03 10:37:11');
