(7,'joke_69c940265a80a','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 20:07:27',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774796847,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"Here\'s a stand-up comedy joke about cats:  \\n\\n\\\"_cats_ are like tiny, fluffy dictators. They walk into a room, sit on your keyboard, knock over your vase, and then stare at you like you\'re the problem. You try to clean up their chaos, but they\\u2019re already plotting their next move. And when you\\u2019re done, they\\u2019re like, \'Ah, you\\u2019ve done your duty. Now, let\\u2019s see\\u2026 do you have a treat? Or are you just a human-shaped dustbin for my hairballs?\'  \\n\\nThe best part? You\\u2019re not even allowed to call them \\u2018cute\\u2019 anymore. It\\u2019s *mandatory*. If you say \\u2018adorable,\\u2019 they\\u2019ll just flick their tail like, \'This is *so* overrated.\' You\\u2019re stuck in a relationship where you\\u2019re the servant, the janitor, and the therapist\\u2014all while they nap in the sun, judging your life from a 30-foot high throne.\\\"  \\n\\n*(Pauses, then deadpan)* \\\"And if you ask them to stop scratching the couch, they\\u2019ll just look at you and say, \'You want me to stop *scratching*? What\\u2019s the alternative? You want me to *not* mark my territory? You\\u2019re asking for a rebellion.\'\\\"\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":119,\"completion_tokens\":873,\"total_tokens\":992}}'),
(8,'joke_69c94131e1f73','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 20:11:51',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774797111,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"Why did the cat get kicked out of the house? Because it was the first one to leave the house and the last one to come back.\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":119,\"completion_tokens\":475,\"total_tokens\":594}}'),
(9,'joke_6_69c94272bebc8','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 20:17:18',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774797437,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"**Setup:** You know you\'ve adopted a cat when you realize they\'re not your friend, they\'re just a furry, independent contractor who charges you for their affection.  \\n\\n**Punchline:** And if you don\'t pay on time, they\'ll knock over your water glass and leave you with a wet spot and a broken heart.\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":124,\"completion_tokens\":992,\"total_tokens\":1116}}'),
(10,'joke_7_69c942ce7a905','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 20:18:46',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774797526,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"**Setup:** \\\"You know you\\u2019ve reached the peak of cat ownership when your furniture is more damaged than your relationship with your significant other.\\\"  \\n**Punchline:** \\\"And the cat? It\\u2019s sitting in the middle of the mess, licking its paw, like it\\u2019s the *host* of the chaos.\\\"  \\n\\n*(Note: This joke leans into the uncensored humor of cats being destructive and indifferent to their own impact, while the punchline adds a touch of dark sarcasm.)*\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":124,\"completion_tokens\":768,\"total_tokens\":892}}'),
(11,'joke_sync_69c942e3ec0ea','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 20:19:06',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774797546,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"**Setup:**  \\n\\\"I tried to teach my cat to use a box as a dining table...\\\"  \\n\\n**Punchline:**  \\n\\\"...but it just turned it into a litter box. Now I have to explain to my guests that the \'art installation\' in the living room is actually a cat\\u2019s version of a portable toilet.\\\"\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":124,\"completion_tokens\":599,\"total_tokens\":723}}'),
(12,'joke_sync_69c94361ad104','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 20:21:15',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774797675,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"**Setup:**  \\n\\\"I was working on my presentation when my cat walked by. I thought it was just curious, but then it started knocking over my notes.\\\"  \\n\\n**Punchline:**  \\n\\\"Turns out, it\'s not just a cat\\u2014it\'s a professional saboteur with a PhD in chaos theory.\\\"\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":124,\"completion_tokens\":937,\"total_tokens\":1061}}'),
(13,'joke_sync_69c9439ad4faa','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 20:22:13',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774797733,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"**Setup:**  \\n\\\"Why did the cat get kicked out of the house?\\\"  \\n\\n**Punchline:**  \\n\\\"Because it was the only one who could knock over the vase without getting a reward.\\\"  \\n\\n**Alternative version (more edgy):**  \\n\\\"I adopted a cat, and now I\'m a millionaire. The cat just sits there and stares at me, but I know it\'s plotting to take over the world. Because it\'s got a PhD in *\'I\'m not doing anything, but you\'re paying for it.\'*\\\"  \\n\\nEither works\\u2014depends on how much you want to lean into the cat\'s perceived laziness.\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":124,\"completion_tokens\":972,\"total_tokens\":1096}}'),
(14,'joke_sync_69c944774101c','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 20:25:48',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774797948,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"**Setup:**  \\n\\\"You know, cats are such independent creatures. They\\u2019ll sit on your keyboard, knock over your water glass, and then act like it\\u2019s *your* fault for not providing enough catnip.\\\"  \\n\\n**Punchline:**  \\n\\\"But when you finally leave the room, they\\u2019ll casually stroll over to the litter box, do their business, and then *poof*\\u2014they\\u2019re back to ignoring you like you\\u2019re a rogue squirrel.\\\"  \\n\\n*(Pause for effect, then deadpan)*  \\n\\\"Turns out, their independence is just a fancy way of saying they\\u2019re lazy and need a nap after every decision.\\\"\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":124,\"completion_tokens\":450,\"total_tokens\":574}}'),
(15,'comedy_vid_6_69c9452c3dfa4','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 20:28:46',1,'{\"status\":\"processing\",\"tip\":\"Get 20x faster image generation using enterprise plan. Click here : https:\\/\\/modelslab.com\\/enterprise\",\"eta\":80,\"message\":\"Request queued for processing. Try to fetch request after estimated seconds.\",\"fetch_result\":\"https:\\/\\/modelslab.com\\/api\\/v6\\/video\\/fetch\\/173305593\",\"id\":173305593,\"output\":[],\"future_links\":[\"https:\\/\\/pub-3626123a908346a7a8be8d9295f44e26.r2.dev\\/generations\\/65f664d0-3856-4e1d-bdf0-9f1defd5c11f-0.mp4\"],\"meta\":{\"num_frames\":81,\"num_inference_steps\":4,\"num_steps\":4,\"num_samples\":1,\"adaptive_resolution\":\"no\",\"init_image\":\"https:\\/\\/app.aistandup.live\\/public\\/templates\\/standup\\/african-male-neon-comedy-lounge.jpg\",\"seed\":751490,\"prompt\":\"A comedian on stage delivering a joke about \\\"You know, cats are such independent creatures. They\\u2019ll sit on your keyboard, knock over your water glass, and then act like it\\u2019s your fault for not providing enough catnip.\\\" \\\"But when you finally leave the room, they\\u2019ll casually stroll over to the litter box, do their business, and then poof\\u2014they\\u2019re back to ignoring you like you\\u2019re a rogue squirrel.\\\" (Pause for effect, then deadpan) \\\"Turns out, their independence is just a fancy way of saying they\\u2019re lazy and need a nap after every decision.\\\" with expressive gestures and timing.\",\"base64\":\"no\",\"webhook\":\"https:\\/\\/app.aistandup.live\\/api\\/aigen\\/saveresponse\",\"track_id\":\"comedy_vid_6_69c9452c3dfa4\",\"temp\":\"no\",\"watermark\":\"no\",\"output_type\":\"mp4\",\"id\":173305593,\"file_prefix\":\"65f664d0-3856-4e1d-bdf0-9f1defd5c11f\",\"output\":[\"https:\\/\\/pub-3626123a908346a7a8be8d9295f44e26.r2.dev\\/generations\\/65f664d0-3856-4e1d-bdf0-9f1defd5c11f-0.mp4\"]}}'),
(16,'comedy_vid_7_69c950177199f','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 21:15:49',1,''),
(17,'joke_u1_202603291727','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 22:27:45',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774805265,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"I brought a cat home, thinking it would be a loyal companion. Turns out, it\'s a tiny tornado with a fur coat and a heart that only warms up when you\'re not in the room. Now I\'m just the snack provider and the emotional support pillow. It\'s like the cat\'s got a hidden camera and a grudge against my presence\\u2014every time I walk into the room, it\'s back to its \\\"I\'m judging you\\\" face, then when I\'m out, it\'s all, \\\"Oh, you\'re not here? Now you\'re my favorite human.\\\"\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":119,\"completion_tokens\":1114,\"total_tokens\":1233}}'),
(18,'joke_u1_202603291732','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 22:32:44',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774805564,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"I got a cat. It\'s not that it\'s ungrateful, it\'s just... it\'s got a lot of opinions. Like, when I bring a new couch home, it sits on it for five minutes, then proceeds to knock it over. I think it\'s trying to tell me something, but I can\'t understand a word. Maybe it\'s saying, \\\"This is my spot, and I\'m not impressed by your new furniture.\\\" I tried to explain that I\'m just trying to improve my living space, but the cat just stares at me like I\'m the one who\'s broken. And then, when I finally give up and let it take over, it\'s like the couch is now its throne, and I\'m just the servant. It\'s not that it\'s ungrateful\\u2014it\'s just... it\'s got a lot of opinions, and I\'m not even allowed to have my own.\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":119,\"completion_tokens\":1099,\"total_tokens\":1218}}'),
(19,'joke_u1_202603291734','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 22:34:28',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774805668,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"\\\"Did you know cats have 2000 times more muscle than humans? That\'s why they can knock over your stuff and then sit there like they own the place. I tried to explain to my roommate that it\'s not the cat\'s fault\\u2014it\'s just the muscle mass. He said, \'Yeah, but you\'re the one who bought the couch.\' I replied, \'I didn\'t buy the couch, I bought a *cat*. It\'s a *different* kind of investment.\'\\\"\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":119,\"completion_tokens\":826,\"total_tokens\":945}}'),
(20,'joke_u1_202603291740','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 22:41:03',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774806063,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"You know you\'re not the only one who\'s ever been alone... cats have been alone for longer. They\'ve been alone since the dawn of time, while we\'ve just been... lonely. And when you finally get a cat, you think you\'ve found a companion, but no\\u2014 they\'re like, \\\"Yeah, you\'re lonely? I\'m just... existing. And I\'m doing it in a 3D box.\\\"\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":119,\"completion_tokens\":407,\"total_tokens\":526}}'),
(21,'joke_u1_202603291752','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 22:53:07',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774806786,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"Why did the cat sit on my keyboard? Because it heard the Wi-Fi password was *password123* and wanted to join the network. But when it finally got online, it just started sending emails to itself\\u2014like, *To: Meow, Subject: I\'m the boss now.* And I\'m like, \\\"Okay, but I\'m still the one paying the bills.\\\"\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":119,\"completion_tokens\":879,\"total_tokens\":998}}'),
(22,'joke_u1_202603291753','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 22:54:11',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774806851,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"I had a cat that thought it was a dog. One day, it brought me a dead mouse and said, \\\"Look, I\'m a hunter!\\\" I was like, \\\"Cool, but you\'re a cat. You don\'t need to act like a dog.\\\" It just stared at me and said, \\\"Well, at least I\'m not a fish.\\\"\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":119,\"completion_tokens\":1208,\"total_tokens\":1327}}'),
(23,'joke_u1_20260329183425','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-29 23:34:33',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774809272,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"\\\"Why did the cat bring a ladder to the party? Because it heard the theme was \'no stairs, just purrs\'\\u2014and it wanted to make sure it could reach the snack table without any *human* interference.\\\"\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":119,\"completion_tokens\":682,\"total_tokens\":801}}'),
(24,'joke_u1_20260330053126','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-30 10:31:38',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774848698,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"**Setup:** Why did the cat bring the litter box into the living room?  \\n**Punchline:** Because it heard the couch was having a sale.\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":124,\"completion_tokens\":1081,\"total_tokens\":1205}}'),
(25,'joke_u1_20260330075449','2026-03-30 10:05:12','2026-03-30 12:54:53',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1774857293,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"Why did the cat sit on the computer? To keep the mice away from the keyboard.\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":177,\"completion_tokens\":249,\"total_tokens\":426}}'),
