(91,'joke_u1_20260401065436','2026-04-01 06:54:52','2026-04-01 11:54:52',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1775026492,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"Here\'s a stand-up comedy joke about instant noodle survival:  \\n\\n\\\"Instant noodles are the ultimate survival food. They\\u2019re like a bag of hope, a cup of water, and a desperate prayer to your taste buds. I once survived a week in a hotel room with nothing but a bag of instant noodles. The hotel provided the water, and I provided the courage. Turns out, the real survival is when you\\u2019re eating noodles and pretending you\\u2019re not starving. But here\\u2019s the kicker\\u2014when the apocalypse comes, and you\\u2019re scrambling to find food, you\\u2019ll be the one yelling, *\'I\\u2019ve got the noodles! I\\u2019ve got the noodles!\'* while the zombies gnaw on your soul. That\\u2019s the *true* survivalist meal: a single cup of broth and a lifetime of regret.\\\"  \\n\\n*Punchline: \\\"And if you\\u2019re lucky, the noodles will be *just* right. Or maybe they\\u2019ll be *completely* wrong. Either way, you\\u2019ll be alive. That\\u2019s the only thing that matters.\\\"*\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":124,\"completion_tokens\":1526,\"total_tokens\":1650}}'),
(92,'joke_u1_20260401065533','2026-04-01 06:55:48','2026-04-01 11:55:48',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1775026548,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"I was on a survival trip and my guide said, \\\"If you ever get lost, just eat instant noodles. They\\u2019re the ultimate survival food.\\\" I said, \\\"What if there\\u2019s no water?\\\" He said, \\\"Then you\\u2019ll survive on noodles and your imagination.\\\" And that\\u2019s exactly what I did. Now I\\u2019m imagining a restaurant, and the noodles are still the same.\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":121,\"completion_tokens\":1377,\"total_tokens\":1498}}'),
(93,'joke_u1_20260401065623','2026-04-01 06:56:32','2026-04-01 11:56:32',2,'{\"object\":\"text_completion\",\"created\":1775026591,\"model\":\"huihui-ai\\/Huihui-Qwen3-8B-abliterated-v2\",\"choices\":[{\"text\":\"I tried to survive on instant noodles for a month. By day three, I was so hungry I started eating the soup packets like they were snacks. I mean, they\\u2019re not even snacks\\u2014they\\u2019re just sad, pre-packaged disasters. But hey, at least I never had to worry about the noodles getting cold. I kept them in my pocket, and if I felt like I was about to die of starvation, I\\u2019d just microwave them and pretend I was in a survivalist camp. Turns out, the real survival skill is not the noodles, but the ability to convince yourself that a cup of broth and a plastic spoon is a gourmet meal. And if you\\u2019re lucky, you\\u2019ll find a nearby tree to use as a windbreak while you chew.\",\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"length\",\"stop_reason\":null,\"prompt_logprobs\":null}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":121,\"completion_tokens\":792,\"total_tokens\":913}}'),
