(110,'comvid_u1_50_20260402','2026-04-02 16:15:25','2026-04-02 11:15:25',2,'{\"status\":\"success\",\"webhook_type\":\"success\",\"track_id\":\"comvid_u1_50_20260402\",\"id\":173628849,\"output\":[\"https:\\/\\/pub-3626123a908346a7a8be8d9295f44e26.r2.dev\\/generations\\/1eb0613c-02fa-47dd-8585-70f35dae9d2a.mp4\"],\"meta\":{\"model_id\":\"ltx-2-3-pro-i2v\",\"prompt\":\"The video starts with the woman in the exact extreme, high-energy pose from image_0.png. She is in active, intense motion: bouncing in place, shaking both hands rapidly, and making direct, wide-eyed contact. The colorful shirt and red sunglasses are dynamic but identical. The camera is locked on a tripod. This intense looping motion continues for 1 second. Suddenly, mid-motion, she briefly becomes still. Her body completely freezes. Only her lips move stiffly to deliver: \'{joke}\'. Her wide-eyed, manic expression is frozen, but her voice is strangely calm. Immediately after, the intense, high-energy looping motion resumes. Maintain perfect identity consistency throughout.\",\"resolution\":\"1920x1080\",\"negative_prompt\":\"blurry, low quality, distorted, extra limbs, missing limbs, broken fingers, deformed, glitch, artifacts, unrealistic, low resolution, bad anatomy, duplicate, cropped, watermark, text, logo, jpeg artifacts, noisy, oversaturated, underexposed, overexposed, flicker, unstable motion, motion blur, stretched, mutated, out of frame, bad proportions\",\"webhook\":\"https:\\/\\/app.aistandup.live\\/api\\/aigen\\/saveresponse\",\"generate_audio\":true,\"duration\":\"8\",\"track_id\":\"comvid_u1_50_20260402\",\"init_image\":[\"https:\\/\\/app.aistandup.live\\/public\\/templates\\/social\\/over-caffeinated-friend.jpg\"]}}'),
