(145,'joke_u1_20260402143040','2026-04-02 14:30:45','2026-04-02 19:30:45',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775140241-9eRybHwxyCX8NzNUcijA\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775140241,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"(Adjusts mic, looks around)\\n\\nSo, life, right? It\'s like that one friend who always says they\'re going to be successful, but then spends their weekends selling handmade dog sweaters on Etsy. \\n\\n(Pause for laughter)\\n\\nSeriously, the optimism! It\'s beautiful. But also... kind of baffling. \\n\\nI spent the whole day trying to figure out if I should order pizza or tacos. It was a major existential crisis. And the only thing that made it better was realizing both were objectively terrible choices. \\n\\n(Shrugs)\\n\\nThat\'s life, folks. Just a series of mildly disappointing decisions and existential dread disguised as lunch.  \\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":153,\"total_tokens\":164,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":153,\"cost\":0.0}'),
(146,'joke_u1_20260402143327','2026-04-02 14:33:32','2026-04-02 19:33:32',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775140407-NeBv7VKNZQsOGq6SeOfp\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775140407,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"(Adjusts mic, looks around)\\n\\nSo, life is like\\u2026 a really elaborate choose-your-own-adventure book. \\n\\n(Pause for chuckle)\\n\\nAnd we\'re all just frantically flipping through the pages, hoping to find a plot twist that\'s actually *good*. \\n\\n(Leans into the mic)\\n\\nBecause honestly? Most of the plot twists are just unexpected bills and awkward family dinners. \\n\\n(Deadpan)\\n\\nAnd the ending? Well, let\'s just say the author hasn\'t finished writing it yet. So, we\'re all just awkwardly holding the manuscript and hoping someone else will decide it\'s a masterpiece. \\n\\n(Shrugs)\\n\\nBut hey, at least we have snacks. Right?  \\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":161,\"total_tokens\":172,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":161,\"cost\":0.0}'),
(147,'joke_u1_20260402143504','2026-04-02 14:35:10','2026-04-02 19:35:10',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775140504-dcpIqF2ChsYOPIMH8Llh\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775140504,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"(Adjusts mic)\\n\\nYou know, life is like a really long, complicated grocery list. You\'re constantly adding things, checking them off, and then realizing you forgot the milk... on Tuesday.  And by the time you get to the end, you\'ve started questioning all your life choices, wondering if you really needed that avocado. \\n\\n(Pause for laughter)\\n\\nSeriously, who needs avocado? It\'s just green mush!  I\'m pretty sure I\'m just here to optimize my fridge for maximum peace of mind.  #LifeIsABuyList #AvocadoRegret #SendHelp\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":129,\"total_tokens\":140,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":129,\"cost\":0.0}'),
(148,'joke_u1_20260402143718','2026-04-02 14:37:25','2026-04-02 19:37:25',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775140638-PQBami4yGwu1P5oh7pKh\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775140638,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"(Adjusts mic, looks around)\\n\\nSo, life, right? It\'s like a really elaborate choose-your-own-adventure book... where every choice leads to slightly different levels of disappointment. \\n\\nI spent three hours last night trying to decide what to have for dinner. I\'m talking meticulously researching recipes, considering dietary restrictions, mentally picturing the perfectly plated meal... and ended up ordering pizza. \\n\\nYou know what? That\'s the brilliance of life. We spend all this time planning the perfect future, agonizing over every little detail, only to realize the best part of it is figuring out how to get a decent pepperoni pizza delivered. \\n\\n(Pause for laughter)\\n\\nAnd that\'s just Tuesday.  \\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":158,\"total_tokens\":169,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":158,\"cost\":0.0}'),
(149,'joke_u1_20260402143922','2026-04-02 14:39:31','2026-04-02 19:39:31',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775140763-nzUunqrkNnqatkm1xHSW\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775140763,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"(Adjusts mic, looks around)\\n\\nYou know, life is like\\u2026 a really long, complicated game of hide-and-seek. \\n\\nLike, I\'m *always* looking for the hiding place, but nobody ever tells you where it is. And the only thing you\'re hiding *from* is probably just the fact that you\'re still trying to figure out how to assemble IKEA furniture. \\n\\nSeriously, I think the instructions are written in ancient hieroglyphics. And the Allen wrench? It\'s judging me.  It doesn\'t *give* you answers, it just sits there, smugly.\\n\\n\\n\\n(Pause for laughter, shrugs)\\n\\nMaybe I\\u2019m just bad at hide-and-seek. Or maybe life *is* designed to be a really elaborate prank.  I\\u2019m starting to think I should just embrace the chaos and wear a silly hat.\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":191,\"total_tokens\":202,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":191,\"cost\":0.0}'),
(150,'joke_u1_20260402144137','2026-04-02 14:41:42','2026-04-02 19:41:42',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775140898-JpxWzJVhDMcXykRJeZTy\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775140898,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"(Adjusts mic, looks around)\\n\\nSo, life, right? It\'s like a really elaborate choose-your-own-adventure book... where every choice leads to a slightly different brand of disappointment. \\n\\nLike, I spent three hours meticulously crafting the perfect email to my boss about a minor inconvenience. Three hours! And the response? \\\"Thanks!\\\" \\n\\nI\'m pretty sure my life is just a series of progressively underwhelming plot twists.  I\'m hoping the final twist is finding a self-cleaning toilet.  That\'s a life goal, people. A *real* life goal.\\n\\n\\n\\n**(Pause for laughter, maybe a slight shrug)**\\n\\n\\n\\nIt\'s just, eventually you realize the point isn\'t the destination... it\'s the existential dread you\'re experiencing while driving to get there.\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":179,\"total_tokens\":190,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":179,\"cost\":0.0}'),
(151,'joke_u1_20260402145129','2026-04-02 14:51:34','2026-04-02 19:51:34',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775141489-0J1K4XStaGi2NHoxa7xj\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775141489,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"**(Stands center stage, adjusts mic)**\\n\\nSo, life, right? It\'s like a really long, complicated scavenger hunt. \\n\\nYou\'re handed a list of \\\"Things To Do\\\" - \\\"Get a job,\\\" \\\"Find love,\\\" \\\"Buy a house,\\\" \\\"Avoid existential dread.\\\" \\n\\nAnd honestly, most of the clues are written in a foreign language and the map is constantly being updated. \\n\\nI\'m pretty sure the person who created this scavenger hunt is just trolling us.  Like, \\\"Oh, you\'re going to find happiness?  Just follow the clues, it\'ll be *easy*.\\\"  \\n\\nYeah, right.  I\'m pretty sure I\'m going to find happiness... buried under a pile of unpaid bills and a crippling fear of pigeons. \\n\\n**(Pauses for laughter)**\\n\\nAnyone else? Anyone feel like this?  Because I\'m starting to think \\\"existential dread\\\" is just a special edition clue with extra confusing instructions.\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":209,\"total_tokens\":220,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":209,\"cost\":0.0}'),
(152,'joke_u1_20260402145216','2026-04-02 14:52:20','2026-04-02 19:52:20',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775141536-TpDuFbIHWrUnZdgkA8yz\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775141536,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"(Adjusts mic)\\n\\nSo, life, right? It\'s like that app you downloaded thinking it would make your life easier. You spend three hours setting it up, tweaking the filters, and then it just... glitches.  Suddenly, you\'re drowning in notifications, and the only thing it\'s reminding you of is things you *should* be doing. \\n\\nAnd then you look around and realize the whole point of the app was to make you feel\\u2026 less\\u2026 overwhelmed?  \\n\\nYeah, life\\u2019s just a really sophisticated, constantly updating, and often malfunctioning app. \\n\\n(Pause for laughter)\\n\\nAnyone else feel that way?  I\'m pretty sure I need a refund.\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":148,\"total_tokens\":159,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":148,\"cost\":0.0}'),
(153,'joke_u1_20260402145508','2026-04-02 14:55:13','2026-04-02 19:55:13',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775141709-1hfnYbLdLV7THLlHr1t4\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775141709,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"(Adjusts mic, looks around)\\n\\nSo, life, right? It\'s like that slow-motion replay of your entire day. You\'re just *walking* through it, watching everything happen to you, and you\'re like, \\\"Wait, did I just spill coffee on my shirt *and* get a passive-aggressive email from my boss *and* accidentally set off the fire alarm trying to make toast?\\\" \\n\\nAnd then you sigh and think, \\\"Well, at least the toast is perfectly golden brown.\\\" \\n\\n(Pause for laughter)\\n\\nI\'m not saying life is *easy*. But I\'m pretty sure the golden brown toast is the only thing keeping me going. It\\u2019s a small victory, folks. A small, perfectly toasted victory.\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":163,\"total_tokens\":174,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":163,\"cost\":0.0}'),
(154,'joke_u1_20260402145523','2026-04-02 14:55:33','2026-04-02 19:55:33',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775141723-WKI0pzgqdrLIeVkUSpaC\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775141723,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"(Adjusts mic)\\n\\nSo, life, right? It\'s like a really elaborate scavenger hunt. You think you know the clues, you\'re following the instructions, and you\'re just *so* close to the prize\\u2026 and then you realize the prize is just a slightly moldy sandwich. \\n\\n(Pause for laughter)\\n\\nAnd the instructions are written in ancient hieroglyphics, only the hieroglyphics are actually just poorly translated Google Translate.  I\'m convinced life is just a really bad, perpetually-delayed online shopping experience.  You order something, it takes forever to arrive, it\'s slightly different from what you expected, and the shipping cost was *astronomical*. \\n\\n(Shrugs)\\n\\nBut hey, at least we have Netflix.  Right?  Right?!\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":168,\"total_tokens\":179,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":168,\"cost\":0.0}'),
(155,'joke_u1_20260402145637','2026-04-02 14:56:42','2026-04-02 19:56:42',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775141797-2oTSxoes62LK7ajXjOPg\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775141797,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"(Adjusts mic)\\n\\nSo, life, right? It\\u2019s just\\u2026 a series of increasingly awkward auditions for roles you didn\\u2019t sign up for. \\n\\nLike, I spent years training to be a barista. Perfectly crafted lattes, artistic foam swans\\u2026 and now I\'m chasing down a rogue sock.  \\n\\nIt\\u2019s a tough gig.  You think you\'ve got it figured out, you\\u2019re coasting on a wave of lukewarm enthusiasm, and then BAM! You realize you\\u2019re allergic to happiness and the plot twist is that your goldfish is judging your entire existence. \\n\\n(leans into the mic)\\n\\nSeriously, that little fish is a harsh critic.  He just stares at me with those beady little eyes and silently judges my life choices. I think he\\u2019s plotting my demise.  It\\u2019s a very fishy situation, you know?\\n\\n\\n\\n**(Pause for laughter)**\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":199,\"total_tokens\":210,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":199,\"cost\":0.0}'),
