(157,'joke_u1_20260402150104','2026-04-02 15:01:08','2026-04-02 20:01:08',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775142064-gDlUGEkDW512OtWaFWLt\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775142064,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"(Adjusts mic)\\n\\nSo, I\'ve been thinking about life lately, right? And it\'s just... weird. Like, we spend so much time *trying* to figure it out, chasing goals, stressing about the future... \\n\\nAnd then you realize the biggest accomplishment you\'ve achieved is successfully microwaving popcorn without burning it. \\n\\n(Beat)\\n\\nSeriously! That\'s a life skill. Don\'t underestimate the power of perfectly warmed popcorn. It\'s a small victory, but a victory nonetheless.  I\'m working on my Olympic-level popcorn skills. Wish me luck.\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":134,\"total_tokens\":145,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":134,\"cost\":0.0}'),
(158,'joke_u1_20260402150320','2026-04-02 15:03:24','2026-04-02 20:03:24',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775142201-WpcswbJHdZJVLWk9RgKs\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775142201,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"(Adjusts mic, looks around)\\n\\nYou know, life. It\'s like a really elaborate choose-your-own-adventure book... except every time you think you\'re about to reach the exciting part, you get a chapter about filing your taxes. \\n\\nSeriously! It\'s all about the mundane details. You spend years chasing dreams, climbing ladders, and finally achieving your goals... and then you realize the biggest challenge is remembering to put the toilet seat down. \\n\\nIt\\u2019s a brutal, beautiful, completely illogical journey. I\\u2019m starting to think the author just really, *really* enjoyed paperwork. \\n\\n(Pause for laughter)\\n\\nAnyone else feel like their life story is just a series of increasingly urgent emails? \\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":161,\"total_tokens\":172,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":161,\"cost\":0.0}'),
(159,'joke_u1_20260402150416','2026-04-02 15:04:22','2026-04-02 20:04:22',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775142256-SRsXzdWdZgvAHJIQZZEY\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775142256,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"(Adjusts microphone, looks out at the audience)\\n\\nSo, I was thinking about life the other day. You know, the big one. And I realized it\'s just a series of things we do to avoid having to explain why we\'re watching paint dry. \\n\\n(Pause for laughter)\\n\\nSeriously! I mean, the existential dread? It\'s just a performance. We\'re all desperately trying to convince ourselves that we\'re making a difference, while simultaneously scrolling through TikTok and judging people\'s outfits. \\n\\nIt\'s like, the universe is saying, \\\"Hey, you\'re here, you\'re breathing, you\'ve got a questionable fashion choice \\u2013 enjoy the ride!\\\" And we\'re all just politely nodding and pretending we\'re deeply contemplating the meaning of it all, while secretly Googling \\\"how to fold a fitted sheet.\\\" \\n\\n(Shrugs) \\n\\nLife. It\'s a beautiful, confusing, and mostly just a lot of laundry.\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":222,\"total_tokens\":233,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":222,\"cost\":0.0}'),
(160,'joke_u1_20260402150434','2026-04-02 15:04:40','2026-04-02 20:04:40',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775142274-xpwPx8wmypICakzQkyt3\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775142274,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"(Adjusts mic, looks around)\\n\\nYou know, life is weird, right? Like, you spend so much time worrying about what other people think, and then you realize most of them are just trying to figure out what *they* think about *you*. \\n\\nIt\'s like a cosmic game of telephone, but with less fun and more awkward silences. \\n\\nAnd the best part? We\\u2019re all just trying to find a good parking spot, and the universe is like, \\\"Nah, you\'re gonna get stuck in traffic for the rest of your days.\\\" \\n\\n(Pause for laughter)\\n\\nSeriously though, you gotta laugh, right? Because if you don\'t, you\\u2019ll just end up questioning all your life choices... which, let\'s be honest, is just a fancy way of admitting you\'re a little lost.\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":180,\"total_tokens\":191,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":180,\"cost\":0.0}'),
(161,'joke_u1_20260402150527','2026-04-02 15:05:32','2026-04-02 20:05:32',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775142328-KMDgPZ1MpkkmjfHbV20G\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775142328,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"(Adjusts mic, looks around)\\n\\nSo, life, right? It\'s basically just a series of increasingly awkward Zoom meetings we never asked for. \\n\\nLike, I spent a solid hour yesterday trying to assemble a bookshelf. Ended up with a pile of particleboard and a newfound appreciation for the structural integrity of pigeons. \\n\\nAnd the worst part? We\'re all just pretending we have it together.  We\'re all going through it.  Like a badly choreographed dance routine nobody invited us to. \\n\\nSeriously, though, what\\u2019s the point?  We\\u2019re all just trying to figure out how to order pizza without accidentally ordering three different kinds of pineapple. It\\u2019s a beautiful, chaotic mess!\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":152,\"total_tokens\":163,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":152,\"cost\":0.0}'),
(162,'joke_u1_20260402150645','2026-04-02 15:06:47','2026-04-02 20:06:47',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775142406-iJ4OymrXW9lIK2Ml4YnY\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775142406,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Human: Life\'s a beautiful, unfolding journey.\\nObject (a rock): Sure, riveting. Just rocks.\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":40,\"completion_tokens\":25,\"total_tokens\":65,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":40,\"completionToken\":25,\"cost\":0.0}'),
(163,'joke_u1_20260402150728','2026-04-02 15:07:34','2026-04-02 20:07:34',2,'{\"id\":\"gen-1775142449-Huu39edJKj5AdxtzE10D\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1775142449,\"model\":\"google-gemma-3n-e2b-it-free\",\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"(Adjusts mic, looks out at the audience)\\n\\nYou know, life. It\'s like a really long, complicated scavenger hunt... but the clues are cryptic, the prize is usually a slightly nicer apartment, and the instructions are written in a language no one understands. \\n\\nAnd the worst part? You spend your whole life trying to decipher the clues, and you\'re still just hopelessly lost. I swear, sometimes I think the universe is just testing us to see how many existential crises we can cram into a single year. \\n\\n(Pause for laughter) \\n\\nSeriously though, it\'s just... a lot. But hey, at least we have coffee. And memes. And the fleeting comfort of believing we\'re doing *something* important, even if that something is just meticulously organizing our sock drawer. \\n\\n(Bows slightly)\\n\\nThank you, you\'ve been a wonderfully confusing audience.\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":null}}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":11,\"completion_tokens\":198,\"total_tokens\":209,\"cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"cache_write_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"video_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":\"0.00000000\",\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":\"0.00000000\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"image_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0}},\"promptToken\":11,\"completionToken\":198,\"cost\":0.0}'),
